{"tid":1262818,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"Henry Cavill / Millie Bobby Brown 合演福爾摩斯兄妹","createTime":"2019-06-28T01:15:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-28T02:43:15.000Z","uid":41343,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"303517391d9af5d97e4aec72d77ffbe25add8f6b","tid":1262818,"uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T01:15:30.000Z","msg":"近年憑藉影集《怪奇物語》（Stranger Things）走紅的童星米莉芭比布朗（Millie Bobby Brown），早在2018年便與傳奇影業簽約主演推理小說《福爾摩斯小妹探案系列》（Enola Holmes Mysteries）的改編電影《福爾摩斯小妹探案》（Enola Holmes），終於在今年二月初，本片確定交由影集《倫敦生活》（Fleabag）導演-哈利布拉畢爾（Harry Bradbeer）執導，而如今亨利卡維爾（Henry Cavill）也傳將加入劇組。<br />\n<br />\n《福爾摩斯小妹探案》原作為南希史賓格（Nancy Springer）所著，該系列小說至今出版六本，以名偵探夏洛克福爾摩斯的14歲妹妹艾諾拉為主人翁，米莉芭比布朗將飾演艾諾拉一角，而根據《綜藝》（Variety）雜誌今天的報導，亨利卡維爾則會在片中扮演夏洛克。海倫娜寶漢卡特（Helena Bonham Carter）先前則確定將扮演他們的母親。<br />\n<br />\n本片交由《奇蹟男孩》（Wonder）編劇傑克索恩（Jack Thorne）執筆劇本，預計於這個夏天正式開拍，明年上映。米莉芭比布朗亦會透過她個人的PCMA製片公司擔任本片的製作人。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://geek-base.toy-people.com/?p=6763\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgeek-base.toy-people.com%2F%3Fp%3D6763&d=CAukz3ZnfWt5Iztj8dmWPGiIh%2BLW8fuN5Q3LPFa5L7A%3D&h=4d8ebfab\" target=\"_blank\">https://geek-base.toy-people.com/?p=6763</a>"},{"pid":"009ecec6a309842e166ee811887564e22cc0aef7","tid":1262818,"uid":249940,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T01:17:41.000Z","msg":"唔拍超人了<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50d7c1f1739580e74b0dcdd870b2b6a3790ef1bf","tid":1262818,"uid":134757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T01:19:21.000Z","msg":"屌呀 咁撚細個就有製片公司"},{"pid":"bdeb75457a492f14388a051da9a8eb574406d3d5","tid":1262818,"uid":14675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T02:41:41.000Z","msg":"筋肉型Sherlock"},{"pid":"1d04c4d01b3dd1b8856afd298ada0696412dac06","tid":1262818,"uid":7311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T02:43:15.000Z","msg":"金田一二三<img src=\"/assets